##Database availability

- Publicly available databases such as Greengens and Silva are available on their respective webpages o, alternatively, already Qiime2-formatted in the Qiime2 forums pages
- Ncbi 16S database is available via FTP (https://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/genomes/refseq/)
- WMdb is available upon reasonable request at matteoDOTsoveriniATwellmicroDOTcom for non-profit intitutions users
